data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with easy access to major highways and ideally situated just minutes from downtown San Antonio, Alamodome,  AT&T center, and the Pearl. This cozy house boasts a modernized kitchen and bathroom, with original hardwood flooring throughout! The living room offers ample space for entertaining, and the dining room can double as an office space for those that work from home. Situated on a spacious lot (with no HOA!) that allows room for another unit/casita/workshop to be built on the property. Schedule your showing today!
